'''Combined with [[fathah]]:'''
<font size="5">пєґЎІ</font> вАФ '''ƒБ'''.


'''Combined with [[kasra]]:'''
<font size="5">пєЇЎІ</font> вАФ '''ƒЂ'''.


'''Combined with [[damma]]:'''
<font size="5">{{ARchar|пєЄ}}ЎІ</font> вАФ '''≈Ђ'''.

